{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember going through, and I looked down a few times, and I saw the water, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was just concentrating that I shouldn't fall through one of these railroad ties to make it to the other side of the bridge.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we got across, and here we come to this nice little city of Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was really a shock to me, you know, to see this city-- these nice homes, you know, with this filigree work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember this so vividly-- and these nice clean curtains, you know, white curtains, on the windows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was like a picture-type of situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we marched in the middle of the road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were so filthy by then, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were black from frostbitten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we must have been quite a sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were marching in the slush in the middle of the road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I remember so vividly, you know, these Austrian women, they were putting children in sleighs on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, children were well-fed with nice hats and scarves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I can only remember these women looking towards the storefronts or the homes, and nobody wanted to look at us, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I looked at these homes, and I said, wouldn't that be wonderful-- if I could just be there for one day and have a piece of bread and wash myself and lay down in a bed, you know, with some clean sheets.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That, that was the only thing I said, you know, I would give my life if I could do this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so we marched through Mauthausen, and we came to a hill.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And on the right side there were these granite quarries where they were cutting granite rock from the mountainside.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
